snippet.title: Potion Party - Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Play alone or together with your family or friends and run your own alchemy store.
Get rid of nasty monsters and upgrade your shop step-by-step until it becomes the world's best potion store. Unlock 11 additional characters with unique abilities to assemble the perfect team in the couch-coop or couch-versus modes.
